**Cursed Civilian** | Unaligned Align - Townsfolk Base Alignment
__Basics__
If the Cursed Civilian is attacked by a lycan or a werewolf, they will turn into a sickly wolf instead of dying.
__Details__
Originally, the Cursed Civilian wins with the townsfolk team, however they may betray their team at some point.
If attacked any other way than by a lycan or a werewolf, the Cursed Civilian will die as usual.
